scenes.description: Elizabeth Rose Bloodflame begins the final wrap-up of the 3D collab.
Gigi Murin shares her closing thoughts and thanks her fans.
The group cheers and celebrates Gigi's message.
Elizabeth Rose Bloodflame shares her closing thoughts, expressing her excitement about being 3D.
Cecilia Immergreen shares her closing thoughts and mentions an upcoming concert.
Raora Fontana shares her closing thoughts, thanking the fans from the bottom of her heart.
The group performs their final chants and says goodbye to the audience.
The group dances as the stream transitions to the end screen.
The final static screen for the 3D collab is shown.
